import React from 'react'
import { Box, Tooltip, IconButton } from '@mui/material'
import {Add} from '@mui/icons-material'

const AddPost = () => {
  return (
    <Box >
        <Tooltip title="Delete">
        <Fab color="primary" aria-label="add">
  <AddIcon />
</Fab>
        </Tooltip>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default AddPost
